# 🔥 Core Master Understanding

> JavaScript was introduced to solve the limitations of static, server-dependent websites by enabling browsers to execute logic locally, respond instantly to user actions, reduce full page reloads, and create dynamic user experiences. Later, Node.js expanded JavaScript beyond browsers into backend development, allowing one language to power full-stack applications.

---

